text: Park Sung-hyun (born 1 January 1983) is a South Korean archer. Park competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics and the 2008 Summer Olympics.Park Seong-HyeonSung- Hyun PARK ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for South Korea Category:Olympic silver medalists for South Korea Category:People from Incheon
